215
00:14:34,501 --> 00:14:36,601
Za prvé, rohovka...

216
00:14:37,131 --> 00:14:38,571
Pak, ledviny...

217
00:14:38,901 --> 00:14:41,901
Ohryzek pošlu do USA.

218
00:14:42,301 --> 00:14:46,031
