250
00:16:58,831 --> 00:17:00,971
Copak se všichni ti lidé vypařili?

251
00:17:01,501 --> 00:17:04,301
<i>To... To nedává smysl.</ i>

252
00:17:04,471 --> 00:17:05,531
Pojď za mnou.

253
00:17:10,131 --> 00:17:11,901
- Jin Hyuku. 
- Hej.

254
00:17:13,131 --> 00:17:14,471
